<script src="/assets/js/booze.js"></script>

<div class="container">
    <br />
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col s3 page-col3 card card-style">
            <div class="card-image waves-effect waves-block waves-light">
                <img class="activator" src="/assets/img/wine.jpg">
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="card-title activator grey-text text-darken-4">The Healthiest Ways To Drink Alcohol<i class="material-icons right">more_vert</i></span>
                <p><a href="https://www.medicaldaily.com/lets-get-drunk-healthiest-ways-drink-alcohol-269583" target="_blank">READ MORE</a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-reveal">
                <span class="card-title grey-text text-darken-4">The Healthiest Ways To Drink Alcohol<i class="material-icons right">close</i></span>
                <p>"Let’s face it, it’s hard seeing the benefits of a healthy diet and exercise when we’re always going
                    out for some drinks with friends. Beer is filling and full of carbs, mixed drinks are too sugary,
                    and wine… well, these are nights of debauchery. How can we drink our alcohol and have flat stomachs
                    too?"</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a class="btn btn-large col s9 modal-trigger blue accent-4" href="#addAlcoholForm">Beers, Shots, or Wines Bro?</a>

        <div class="col s9 page-col9">
            <h4>Booze Tracker</h4>
            <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover compact" id="boozeTable">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Booze Name</th>
                        <th>Servings</th>
                        <th>Calories</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
            </table>
            <div id="addAlcoholForm" class="modal">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <h4>What are you drinking?</h4>
                    <form>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="input-field col s12">
                                <input id="drink" type="text" class="validate">
                                <label for="drink">Booze Name</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="input-field col s6">
                                <input id="calories" type="number" class="validate">
                                <label for="calories">Calories</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="input-field col s6">
                                <input id="servings" type="number" class="validate">
                                <label for="servings">Servings</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <a href="#!" class="modal-close waves-effect btn-flat">Close</a>
                    <button id="submitDrink" class="modal-close waves-effect blue accent-4 waves-blue btn-flat white-text">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>